# aws-eks-no-public-cluster-access
# Public API endpoint is intentional for this demo cluster to allow kubectl access.
# In production, restrict public_access_cidrs to known IPs or disable public access entirely.
AVD-AWS-0040

# aws-ec2-no-public-ip-subnet
# Public subnets require map_public_ip_on_launch for EKS public node group to function.
AVD-AWS-0164

# aws-ec2-no-public-egress-sgr
# Unrestricted egress is required for EKS nodes to pull container images and reach AWS APIs.
AVD-AWS-0104
